For this goal, the Seebeck coefficient of the PEDOT:PSS-Te(Cux) hybrid system is plotted as a function of the conductivity (Fig 3b) and fit to the Kang-Snyder Charge Transport model18. We observe that the experimental data lie on the s = 1 CT model curve (Fig 3b) with σE0T=5.47S∕cm\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
